                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.51/968: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bundy</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-08-07T16:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 7, 1919, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your August 4, 1 p.m.</p>
                <p>There are no developments known to the Department making a change of policy
                    advisable at this time. You may repeat suggestion as outlined in Department’s
                    May 20, 6 p.m.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
